author: Al Jazeera
title: China reports no new coronavirus deaths for first time
description: Cases in mainland China have been dwindling since March, but it faces a second wave of infections from overseas.
content:
China reported no new deaths from the coronavirus on Tuesday, for the first time since authorities began publishing figures in January.
